# IOT With Apache Spark and Bahir 

## MQTT

A messaging protocol for sending metrics. 

Environment: https://github.com/lresende/bahir-iot-demo

## Apache Bahir

Connectors for multiple streaming platforms 

https://bahir.apache.org/

## Patterns

 - Remote control
 - Security analysis 
 - Edge Analytics
 - Historical Data Analysis
 - Distributed Platforms

## MQTT - M2M/iot Connectivity Protocol

  - Pub sub 
  - Lots of clients 
  - Small client overhead

## MQTT

 - At most once 
 - Talks to a broker

